{"id":369927,"date":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":2}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"118","ytitle":"","mtitle":"句句山歌如蜜甜","ftitle":"","authors":["周俊炘"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"安卫省宣城中学　周俊炘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银河星星挂满天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肚里山歌万万千，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日出唱到月亮现，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“跃进山歌”唱不完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一唱肥料堆成山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二唱水库发了电，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三唱荒坡穿绿衫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四唱粮食胀破圈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"句句山歌如蜜甜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱得老汉变青年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱得青年猛劲添，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越唱心里越是甜。"}]}